race.comment: MAMUSHKA (2) sent north at her second run back when a tiring fifth over 1300m at the Gold Coast behind Poster Girl. Set to bounce back from the inside gate and should prove too strong for these. CINSAULT (3) kicked off her campaign with a tough win two runs back. Big jump in grade when a close-up fourth over 1400m at Randwick in BM78 grade. A repeat showing will see her hard to stop. SIEBERT (7) talented filly who gets a much better set up for this fourth-up. No match for Miss Busslinger from the sticky draw when second over 1350m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Leading prospect with the sharp weight drop. TEQUILA BABY (1) failed to handle the heavy (8) going when a struggling seventh over 1200m at Rosehill in Midway class. On the quick backup and can bounce back on the firmer surface.
